        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/independent-commission-on-freedom-of-information-report-lord-burns-message">Independent Commission on Freedom of Information report: Lord Burns' message</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
