</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="ICFOI" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/42022/s465_IER-TrainingDocuments-Jan14.JPG"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2016-03-21">21 March 2016</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Independent report</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/publications/independent-commission-on-freedom-of-information-report">Independent Commission on Freedom of Information report</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>This independent report to government reviews the Freedom of Information Act 2000 as it has developed over the past 10 years.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  brand--cabinet-office">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="MCO" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/42024/s465_Matt_Hancock_May2015_GOVUK.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2016-03-01"> 1 March 2016</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Statement to Parliament</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/speeches/open-and-transparent-government">Open and transparent government</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Matt Hancock laid a written statement in Parliament on the Independent Commission on Freedom of Information’s final report.</p>
</div></div>


